Innovation Capability Analysis — PIPRF v1.0
When Knowledge Does Not Translate into Practice: Innovation Readiness as a Missing Capability Layer in Constrained Pharmaceutical Systems
________________________________________
📋 Overview
This repository contains the complete analytical code, de-identified dataset, and supplementary materials for a cross-sectional study of 303 pharmaceutical professionals examining the co-variation structure among IP literacy, innovation attitudes, innovation readiness, and reported innovation practice in a transitional pharmaceutical system.
Target Journal: Research Policy / Nature Human Behaviour / Technovation
Study Design: Cross-sectional observational survey
Data Collection: 10 March – 15 April 2026
Ethics Approval: Manara University (MU-URO-26-02)
________________________________________
